# Review Pipeline Flow — Implementation Plan

## How It Works

### Dispatch Logic
[_do_renew_style()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#1320-1758) reads the selected style JSON → checks `"pipeline"` field:
- `"narrative"` (or missing) → existing flow (unchanged)
- `"review"` → new `_do_renew_review()` worker

### Review Flow (10 steps)

```
Step 1: Concat text
Step 2: extract_blueprint() — same shared prompt, returns product_evaluation
Step 3: recommend_framework() — rank 8 review frameworks → popup user chọn
Step 4: check_blueprint() — audit data vs framework's evaluation_focus
Step 5: convert_units() — Python function, US/EU
Step 6: create_review_outline() — Hook/Body/End outline
Step 7: audit_outline() — reuse existing
Step 8: write_review_chapter() × N — uses NEW prompt (system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt)
Step 9: verify_facts() — fact-check + unit check
Step 10: Merge → FULL_SCRIPT.txt
```

